Table oms.CarrierDO

List of all carriers and additional properties.

Columns 

References[1] Column Type Constraints[2] Default Comment
id bigint PK, UNIQUE, NOT_NULL  
modificationDate timestamp without time zone  
name varchar(50) UNIQUE, NOT_NULL The name of the carrier. Example "DHL" 
trackingUrl varchar(255) The tracking URL used by the carrier. Example "http://nolp.dhl.de/nextt-online-public/report_popup.jsp" 
version integer  
cargoCompany varchar(75) The name of the company that is accepting physical return of products. Used for return logistics. Example "Deutsche Post AG" 
cargoCenter varchar(75) The name of the recipient for physical returns. Used for return logistics. Example "Parcel center 93" 
IdentCodeGenerationBeanDefDO identCodeGenerationBeanDefRef integer The ident code generation implementation that is used by the carrier.
